Likewise, this Strategy seeks to place the EU in the lead of the global fight against antisemitism. 

The EU will use all available tools to call on partner countries and international organisations to combat antisemitism in the EU neighbourhood and beyond. 
 
#No2Antisemitism https://t.co/x8rTyT3mtN

This new Strategy is articulated around three pillars: 

▪️ Preventing and combating all forms of antisemitism. 

▪️ Protecting and fostering Jewish life in the EU. 

▪️ Education, research and Holocaust remembrance. 
 
#No2Antisemitism https://t.co/rvjgYkXQMO

Every second European considers antisemitism a problem. 

We must create an inclusive society based on equality and respect, free from antisemitism and any form of discrimination. 
 
Antisemitism is incompatible with the EU’s core values. 
 
#No2Antisemitism https://t.co/CSS85uL56R

Today, we are presenting our first-ever EU Strategy on combating antisemitism and fostering Jewish life.  

As part of the EU’s work tackling racism and with antisemitism worryingly on the rise, we are determined to put an end to it.  

#No2Antisemitism
